02:12.850 --> 02:13.872
you mean..

02:14.188 --> 02:16.860
he's gonna be-be my-my stepfather?

02:20.553 --> 02:22.276
And you!

02:22.855 --> 02:24.968
You're gonna be my..

02:25.950 --> 02:27.513
He's gonna be my..

