A few hours?

05:10.350 --> 05:14.352
Good.
I.. mean.. have fun with the hoops and what not.

05:19.688 --> 05:22.177
Now it's my turn to kiss you.

05:24.490 --> 05:27.470
Now it's my turn to kiss you.

05:28.598 --> 05:31.835
Now it's my turn to throw up.

05:33.819 --> 05:35.969
